<BaseLayout title="Dataset Preparation for LoRA Training" description="Prepare safe, clean, permission-safe datasets for LoRA training." canonicalPath="/lora/dataset-preparation/"><article class="content-section article-body"><h1>Dataset Preparation for LoRA Training</h1><p>A good dataset is consistent, clean, and legally usable. Prefer original or licensed images, remove duplicates, and include useful variation in pose, camera, lighting, and background.</p><p>Separate concepts when possible. A dataset that mixes outfit, face, location, and style without clear captions can make the LoRA hard to control.</p></article></BaseLayout>
